<note n="0371004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0371004">「勝」，底本作「朦」，據北新627號改。</note>
<note n="0372001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0372001">「經」，底本無，據北新627號補。</note>
<note n="0372002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0372002">「靈」，底本無，據北新627號補。</note>
